text: right Kārlis Leiškalns (born August 10, 1951) is a Latvian politician born in Jūrmala.www.cvk.lv He is a Deputy of the Saeima and a member of the People's Party. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:People from Jūrmala Category:Democratic Center Party of Latvia politicians Category:Latvian Way politicians Category:People's Party (Latvia) politicians Category:Honor to serve Riga politicians Category:Deputies of the 5th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 6th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 7th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 9th Saeima
